*
*---- act defproc: std::cells::INVX1<> -----
* raw ports:  A Y Vdd GND
*
.subckt _0_0std_0_0cells_0_0INVX1 A Y Vdd GND
*.PININFO A:I Y:O Vdd:I GND:I
*.POWER VDD Vdd
*.POWER GND GND
*.POWER NSUB GND
*.POWER PSUB Vdd
*
* --- node flags ---
*
* Y (combinational)
*
* --- end node flags ---
*
M0_N Vdd A Y Vdd p W=3U L=0.6U
M1_N GND A Y GND n W=1.5U L=0.6U
.ends
*---- end of process: INVX1<> -----
*
*---- act defproc: std::cells::NAND2X1<> -----
* raw ports:  A B Y Vdd GND
*
.subckt _0_0std_0_0cells_0_0NAND2X1 A B Y Vdd GND
*.PININFO A:I B:I Y:O Vdd:I GND:I
*.POWER VDD Vdd
*.POWER GND GND
*.POWER NSUB GND
*.POWER PSUB Vdd
*
* --- node flags ---
*
* Y (combinational)
*
* --- end node flags ---
*
M0_N Vdd A Y Vdd p W=3U L=0.6U
M1_N Vdd B Y Vdd p W=3U L=0.6U
M2_N GND A #3 GND n W=3U L=0.6U
M3_N #3 B Y GND n W=3U L=0.6U
.ends
*---- end of process: NAND2X1<> -----
*
