xinvs_50_6 invs_50_6_aA out_50_6 Vdd GND _0_0std_0_0cells_0_0INVX1
xinvs_51_6 invs_51_6_aA out_51_6 Vdd GND _0_0std_0_0cells_0_0INVX1
